<text id="02-output-contract" title="Python FastAPI — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>Output schema for the subagent applying python-fastapi. Encodes required boolean checks against the artefact under review.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema fragment)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ['thin_route_no_orm', 'pydantic_in_out', 'asyncsession_per_task', 'openapi_snapshot_present'],
  "properties": {
    "thin_route_no_orm": { "type": "boolean" },
    "pydantic_in_out": { "type": "boolean" },
    "asyncsession_per_task": { "type": "boolean" },
    "openapi_snapshot_present": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>thin_route_no_orm</item>
      <item>pydantic_in_out</item>
      <item>asyncsession_per_task</item>
      <item>openapi_snapshot_present</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "thin_route_no_orm": true,
  "pydantic_in_out": true,
  "asyncsession_per_task": true,
  "openapi_snapshot_present": true
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates green; methodology applied.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "thin_route_no_orm": false,
  "pydantic_in_out": false,
  "asyncsession_per_task": false,
  "openapi_snapshot_present": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-thin-routes).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
